<dl id="sd1038e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="sd1" href="#sd1038e">SD1 (VI.A)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/sd1all.htm#sd1038e"> 38(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> borrowed so much he had 0 to pay,</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Hateful is he who <mark>borrows so much that he has nothing to pay</mark>. <small> T.R. Roberts, <a name="POW2" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#POW2"><cite title="source">The Proverbs of Wales</cite></a> (1909) 28</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
